{"tid":1382925,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（證視聽）好多人話啲官方相片上警棍加索帶張相係假／唔合理","createTime":"2019-07-29T14:51:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T15:09:30.000Z","uid":47524,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"96f1018341d7eeb10cde26d34ad3e136f76e12f8","tid":1382925,"uid":47524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:51:48.000Z","msg":"又或者原本張相無虛位，噫家官方張相可以有虛位SIP到條繩之類去質疑，<br />\n其實唔講佢咁做出發點同有無可能做到佢所講嗰個效果；<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">問題唔係在於是咪索帶／金屬, 或者加索帶嘅用途；<br />\n應該喺係警棍上加料係咪合理／合法吧？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果加三條索帶係官方認證嘅標準配備, 請警方代表澄清：咁加多十條, 二十條得唔得,？加水喉碼又得唔得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n而得咁樣加／減標準武力配備邊個話事, 警察通例有無寫明?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果唔得嘅話, 佢官方張相涉事嗰位警員額外加索帶係咪犯咗警察通例/法例?<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>PS: 其實佢解釋嗰個用途，用條像根都得啦, 點解要用索帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span>"},{"pid":"c5ec31890c03cbccee9d94c85fe441426566e741","tid":1382925,"uid":47524,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:02:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"433726723134bdb0a43ebab106d0608e406d447d","tid":1382925,"uid":438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:04:10.000Z","msg":"而家軍政府警棍裝釘你都吹佢唔脹"},{"pid":"1b0eb086d05ce9b531e31562ba46ad46c1e88dd8","tid":1382925,"uid":47524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:09